Class Panel

java.lang.Object
org.example.RealEstate
org.example.Panel
All Implemented Interfaces:
PanelInterface, PropertyInterface
public class Panel extends RealEstate implements PanelInterface
Represents a panel-type real estate property.

This class extends RealEstate by adding specific attributes such as floor number and insulation status, and implements the PanelInterface to provide additional behavior.
